Oakley tried to compete by selling their products

00:02:30.960 --> 00:02:37.460
outside Luxotca's retail outlets but failed,
following which Luxottica bought Oakley in

00:02:37.460 --> 00:02:45.720
2007 for 2.1 billion dollars along with 16%
premium over the existing share price.

